TITLE: Updating NgRx Packages with Angular CLI (Shell)
DESCRIPTION: This shell command utilizes the Angular CLI (`ng update`) to update the `@ngrx/store` package specifically to version 15. Running this command also triggers available NgRx migration schematics, which help automate code adjustments required due to breaking changes. Requires Angular CLI version 15.x or higher.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ngrx/platform/blob/main/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/migration/v15.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
