DESCRIPTION: Shows how to refactor the `MoviesPageComponent` to leverage NgRx Store. The component now injects the `Store`, selects the relevant state (`movies$`) as an Observable, and dispatches an action (`[Movies Page] Load Movies`) in `ngOnInit` to trigger the data loading process, delegating the side effect to NgRx Effects.
