TITLE: Reading ComponentStore State with Selectors
DESCRIPTION: Uses `ComponentStore` selectors to derive and expose state values or aggregate them into a view model (`vm$`) observable for the template. Selectors provide reactive access to the state. Component outputs (`@Output()`) can also be derived directly from state changes using selectors and observables.
