TITLE: Testing MovieStore with Signals
DESCRIPTION: Tests the `MoviesStore`'s `load` method with a Signal as input. It simulates scenarios where the studio changes, testing the store's response. The test uses `fakeAsync` to control time, `signal` to provide the studio name, and `effect` for debugging. Dependencies: Jest, @angular/core, @angular/core/testing.
