TITLE: Defining withTotalEntities Feature with props (Post-Version 19) - NgRx Signals TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code demonstrates the updated pattern for defining a SignalStoreFeature in NgRx v19+, replacing the deprecated 'computed' property with 'props'. It utilizes the new 'EntityProps' type from '@ngrx/signals/entities'. The function takes an Entity type and an 'entities' collection and returns a feature exposing computed props such as the entity total. Dependencies include @ngrx/signals and @ngrx/signals/entities. The migrated code ensures compatibility with the latest API.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ngrx/platform/blob/main/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/migration/v19.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
