TITLE: Managing rxMethod Lifecycle with Injector - NgRx Signals - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Explains the automatic cleanup of reactive methods within their creation injector context. It shows how to provide an explicit `injector` option when calling a reactive method from a different injection context to ensure proper cleanup.
